# <c/note>

A code‑styled notes app built to organize code snip-its.

## What it does
- Sign up / log in / log out
- Add, view, edit, delete notes
- Each note can have a tag, title, body
- Basic session auth

## Tech
Node.js • Express • EJS • MongoDB (Mongoose) • CSS

## Run it
```bash
npm install
# create .env file with:
# MONGODB_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/cnote
# SESSION_SECRET=anything-long
# PORT=3000
npm start
```
Open http://localhost:3000

## Structure
```
models/   # Mongoose schemas
routes/   # Express route files
views/    # EJS templates
public/   # styles.css, scripts
server.js # app entry
```

## Future ideas
- Password hashing
- Tag filtering
- Dark mode
- Markdown notes